divs: Sighting DetailsNotice a light in the sky...looked like a jet way out and then I noticed erratic jumping and side to side movement...go my 135 mm lens and started taking pictures...they are pixelated somewhat but are clear enough to see the object. I would estimate the object to be at 60,000 to 80,000 ft up.
Summary: looked like a jet ....way out and then it started to jump side to side and up and down
